  1314 					;Hmm, we shifted out everything... must be zero; reset exponent. This
  1315 					;is critical since Atari Basic depends on the exponent being zero for
  1316 					;a zero result.
  1317 DC27			underflow:
  1318 DC27 4C 43 DA			jmp		fp_clc_zfr0
